y":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"等睇東方不敗加速力大陸文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"以前有個post講阿青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個連登仔有條公式咁<br />\n最後話阿青快過F22 30倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"想補充多一點<br />\n東方不敗講過天下武功 無堅不摧 唯快𣎴破<br />\n而阿青既速度係快過F22 三十倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下以物理學分析<br />\n書入面有咁既一段<br />\n只聽得阿青叫道：「范蠡，你在哪裡？」范蠡向西施瞧了一眼，朗聲道：「阿青，我在這裡。」<br />\n「裡」字的聲音甫絕，嗤的一聲響，門帷從中裂開，一個綠衫人飛了進來，正是阿青。<br />\n<br />\n呢到得知阿青一聽到聲就飛入黎<br />\n假設阿青同西施所處既館娃宮中心距離係1km<br />\n人體極限反應時間係0.1s<br />\nInitial velocity 係0ms-1<br />\n<br />\nS=ut+1/2at^2<br />\n可以得知阿青既加速值係200000ms-2<br />\n而阿青體重應該係50kg<br />\nF=ma<br />\nF=10000000N<br />\n阿青一擊既力量係大約等同於比二百部大貨車重砸<br />\nV=u+at<br />\nV=20000ms-1<br />\nF22最高速係670ms-1<br />\n阿青既速度係佢既29.85倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a045f073c7592eaae49bce19b65b4baebeda37bb","tid":883674,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"石破天速度快過飛機"},{"pid":"753367bb402c6c6ba640a0d3861fc8bf9fdf1cac","tid":883674,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"解釋梯雲縱原理"},{"pid":"58f6e731d9db701b10381fc0a10aac241146c3ea","tid":883674,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:06:22.000Z","msg":"要搵柳田理科雄(《空想科學》系列作者) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aac6e7509d1fce6584b81ddf26c713e7a8ae914","tid":883674,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}